@LG

Welcome to what web-based and print solvers have always experienced: the title up front every Sunday. Just making the experience consistent, IMO. 

The next day's puzzle drops at 10pm Eastern for every day of the week except Sunday and Monday, which drop at 6pm Eastern. If you notice, the stats are always a bit wonky if you solve before the calendar catches up, meaning the daily stat continues to show the current day and you have to click through to the week's stats to see info for the one you just solved. Inconsistently, the stats roll over to the following week on Sunday nights once the next day's puzzle drops. 🤷‍♀️
